text: Alan Osmond is a member of The Osmonds singing family. Excluding Virl and Tom Osmond (the two oldest members of the Osmonds who were not members due to hard of hearing), Alan was the oldest member of the Osmonds. Alan was briefly in a relationship with Karen Carpenter. Category:Musicians from Utah Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:People from Ogden, Utah
title: Alan Osmond
